definition.text: There was an unexpected error and the process was shut down.

paragraphs.text: While running at the TS, the process where this error poped up encountered and unexpected error that forced the TS to shut the process down. The Task might still be running other not affected processes, but if all the processes stop running or this was the only one, then they Task itself might have stopped too.
In the following section you will find the specific information received when this error occured.
You will only see it if you opened this page as a result of the error actually happening.
